is used in preference to <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རིར་</span>, and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བུ་ལ་</span> “to the boy” in preference to <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བུར་</span>.</p>","title":""}]}
